### ✅ Code Integration
The Analytics component is properly integrated in the application:

**File: `src/App.jsx`**
- Import statement (line 2): `import { Analytics } from '@vercel/analytics/react';`
- Component usage (line 120): `if (noLayout) return <>{routes}<Analytics /></>;`
- Component usage (line 122): `return <Layout>{routes}<Analytics /></Layout>;`

The implementation follows the official Vercel documentation for React/Vite applications, placing the `<Analytics />` component at the root level to track all page views and user interactions.

